<template>
  <v-dialog width="30%" v-model="showDialogCreate">
    <v-card>
      <v-card-title>{{ title }}</v-card-title>
      <v-card-text>
        <v-text-field color="#325d79" :label="'Nombre de ' + this.variable" outlined></v-text-field>

        <v-text-field color="#325d79" label="Telefono" outlined v-if="$route.name == 'users'"></v-text-field>

        <v-text-field color="#325d79" label="Correo" outlined v-if="$route.name == 'users'"></v-text-field>

        <v-text-field color="#325d79" label="Contraseña" type="password" outlined v-if="$route.name == 'users'"></v-text-field>

        <v-select color="#325d79" :items="roles" label="Rol de Usuario" outlined v-if="$route.name == 'users'"></v-select>

        <v-text-field
          color="#325d79"
          :label="'Descripción de ' + this.variable"
          outlined
          v-if="$route.name == 'piscicolas'"
        ></v-text-field>

        <v-text-field
          color="#325d79"
          :label="'Ubicación de ' + this.variable"
          outlined
          v-if="this.variable == 'Piscícola'"
        ></v-text-field>
        <v-text-field color="#325d79" label="Unidad de Medida" outlined v-if="this.variable == 'Sensor'"></v-text-field>
      </v-card-text>
      <v-card-actions vuetify-center>
        <v-btn text color="orange" dark class="pa-auto ml-auto"  @click="showDialogCreate=false">CANCELAR</v-btn>
        <v-btn text color="orange" dark class="px-6 mr-auto">CREAR</v-btn>
      </v-card-actions>
    </v-card>
  </v-dialog>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  props: {
    title: {
      type: String
    },
    variable: {
      type: String
    },
    roles: {
      type: String
    },
    value: {
      type: Boolean
    }
  },
  computed: {
    showDialogCreate: {
      get() {
        return this.value;
      },
      set(v) {
        this.$emit("input", v);
      }
    }
  }
};
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped></style>
